sources.description:
A Gripping Journey of Love, Betrayal, and Survival in Colonial America!
HILARITY IN HIGH GEAR!  Sid Melton stars as a taxi driver dealing with nutty passengers and a nagging wife. 

Original title: Stop That Cab (1951) 

Original Black & White version https://youtu.be/A9gW8Odyf54

Director: Eugenio de Liguoro
Writers: Walter Abbott, Louella MacFarlane
Stars: Sid Melton, Iris Adrian, Marjorie Lord, Tom Neal
Genres: Colorized classics, Comedy, Crime
